Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(灵感源于真实事件)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳 你的名字蕴含柔和之意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine. There is a softness in your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不会顽强抵抗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you will not be too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我谈一谈 可以自救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can help yourself by talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不谈的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I will not stop to hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你告诉我我想知道的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十二小时没休息了 你不想睡觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seventy-two hours without rest. Don't you want to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不和我说话 折磨就永不停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't speak to me, this will never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六名学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a sixth student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我他们的名字 否则你就重回冰水里泡着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me their name, or you're going back in the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没什么可告诉你的 - 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have nothing to say to you! - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...你现在安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在安全了 你回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're safe. You're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是我 我是克里斯汀 - 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's me. It's Christian. - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,100)}{\fs40\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}新    风    貌{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,190)}{\fs14\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}第一季第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他们我正在提起诉讼 他们却什么都没说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you told them I was suing, and they had nothing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要明白你发起的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you need to understand what you have started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Started?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没想着发起诉讼 我要毁了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't start it. I'm going to ruin them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 可可... - 皮埃尔和保罗违反了我们签署的合同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Coco-- - Pierre and Paul violated my contract
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们未经我的同意 就将香奈儿5号香水的生产转移到了美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they moved production of Chanel No. 5 to America without my consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背着我做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要由法庭来决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's for a court to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会涉及到进攻和反击 以及...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will be attack and counterattack and--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的 雷奈 你是要做好自己的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goddamn it, René. Are you going to do your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我得回去替你做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or do I have to come back home and do it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我安排了一场午餐 她们是瑞士最富有的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have organized a lunch with the wealthiest women in Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她们喜欢你 她们会付给你很多钱 让你给她们提供服装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they like you, they will pay you a lot of money to dress them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 很高兴见到你 - 你好 你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello. Nice to meet you. - Hello. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们还没安排你们入座吗  - 还没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have they not seated you? - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请帮我们都安排在我那桌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. Seat us all at my table, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 小姐 我能跟你说句话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly, mademoiselle. And may I have a quick word?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你的账单...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mademoiselle, your account--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没时间讨论这个 我向你保证 我会支付的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have time to discuss this. You have my word. I will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上安排 这是一个很重要的午餐 让开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please now, this is an important lunch. Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈的身体状况如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, how is André faring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天前 他和嘉贝拉已抵达巴黎 他的治疗已经开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He and Gabrielle arrived in Paris a few days ago. His treatment has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望一切顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fingers crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩是我仅剩的亲人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those two are all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱他们胜过这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love them more than the world itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有照片吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孙子 孙女们的照片都在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My grandchildren are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 当然有 他们的肖像都裱起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yes. Yes, of course. Their portraits are getting framed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得问一下 那位女士是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must ask, who is that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远处角落里的那个女人 从我们一坐下就一直盯着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The woman in the far corner staring at you since we sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 亲爱的 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coco, darling. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她在向你招手 - 好久不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's waving at you. - It's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 可可 真不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darling, Coco. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 可可... - 似乎还挺执着的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Coco! Coco! - Seems insistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很执着 不是吗 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, she is, isn't she? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看着 你最好过去打个招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's watching. You'd better go over and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳精疲力竭 还处于脱水状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine is dehydrated and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要喂她简单的食物 因为她很可能得了溃疡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to feed her simple foods, because she most likely has ulcers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 但还有别的方面出了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but there's-- Something else is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她常常不知道我是谁或她在哪里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She often doesn't know who I am or where she is--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但饥饿和营养不良 导致的影响是很复杂的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but starvation and malnutrition, you know, the effects are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那些从集中营回来的人身上 看到了多种症状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're seeing multiple symptoms in those who have returned from the camps,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些病历中 还有因创伤引起的健忘症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and in some cases, there is amnesia caused by trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她会恢复记忆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But her memory will return?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过重要的是不要逼她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although it is essential that she'd not be pushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保她好好休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make sure she rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Dior,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳遭受了极大的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine has suffered greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饥饿能使人发疯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Starvation can drive people mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种痛疼得让人难以忍受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is an excruciating pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不仅会造成身体伤害 还会造成头脑和精神伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It really damages the body but also the mind, the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it slowly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每隔几天就会来看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll check on her again every couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制访客人数 可以的话 最好不要见客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Limit visitors. Best to have none if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让她看到我担心的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want her to see me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在得去见维格鲁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have your meeting with Vigouroux now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去 我不可能去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can manage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 早知她要回来 我决不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I would never have made a leap if I'd have known
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒险创业 这是个奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that she was going to return. It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萨克先生给你的这次机会也是一个奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Monsieur Boussac giving you this chance is also a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀 不要浪费这次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christian, don't waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在凯瑟琳回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine is home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是最重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该为自己感到骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should be proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你必须做对你有利的事 - 知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You must do what's good for you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂 - 请问这里是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello. - Have I reached
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀迪奥家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the home of Christian Dior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 这里是迪奥的住所 - 凯瑟琳回来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. This is the Dior residence. - Has Catherine returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉 凯瑟琳  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry, Catherine? - Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想找她 麻烦了 - 不行 不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I would like to speak to her, please. - No, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你确定吗  - 不可以 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you sure? - No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝不会相信 我离开马德里时遇到了多大的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't believe the trouble I had getting out of Madrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英国大使馆的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, those people at the British Embassy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所有人都只关心 我去过哪里 我知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}every one of them, all they cared about was where I'd been, what I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问了我很多问题 真的累死人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So many questions. It was really quite exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很无聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 不 这绝对是一种折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tedious? No, it was absolute torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但你毫发无损地离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, well, you made it out in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是午餐时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦敦会是你更想去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that London would be a more desirable place for you to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我们在马德里的那次不幸事件后 我被贴上了叛徒的标签\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, after our little tango in Madrid, I was labeled a traitor, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在英国的家人都和我断绝了关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my family in England, they all disowned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在我都听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, now I'm all yours, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真走运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lucky me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我这里怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what it's like here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的瑞士人似乎都很...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All these Swiss people seem so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔莎 别打坏主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get any ideas, Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正努力保持低调 你也应该这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to keep a low profile. You should as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's still dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国政府是不是在追捕你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is the French government after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lower your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想让我不透露我所知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want me to keep quiet about what I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不确保我得到你承诺我的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why don't you just make sure I get what you promised me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 就是为了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There it is. This is about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你在马德里说过 只是钱而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darling, you said it yourself in Madrid, it's just money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当施帕茨把钱花光时 你就是这么跟我说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you told me when Spatz spent it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说:“我可以给你更多的钱” 然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said, "I can get more." And then--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我全心全意给予的灵感与桌布作对比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then you compared my heart and soul to a tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是有意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照顾我 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just look after me, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事可以以吻封缄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could be sealed with a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要恭喜你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations are definitely in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个风险项目 你的公司...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This venture, your house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太清楚你对布萨克先生说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not well informed as to what you said to Monsieur Boussac,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他以前从未给任何个人投过这么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he has never before invested this much money in any one individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟热龙说了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you told Lelong yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要离开他 他一定会怒不可遏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He must be beside himself that you're leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没说 但我会说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet. But I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你得马上跟他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you must do it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀 我们必须要完成所有的文件工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christian, we have to finish the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇佣裁缝 女裁缝 模特和员工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hire the tailors, the seamstress. Hire the models, the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有选址 位置是非常重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find the location. Location is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萨克想要引人注目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boussac wants something larger than life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是更私密 更私人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking something a little more intimate, more personal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够表达我专为少数女性提供服装的愿望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something that expresses my desire to dress a few women exquisitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 但经营规模还是要大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. But it still needs to be on a grand scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萨克希望的 不仅是只为少数女性提供服装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Boussac will want something more than a few women dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你知道这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I will need a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不确定你是否知道 但... - 你妹妹从恐怖的集中营回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not sure whether you know, but-- - Your sister is back from the horrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 克里斯汀 这太好了 她怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It's wonderful, Christian. How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在适应中 但需要一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's adjusting, but it will take a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是了不起的壮举啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an amazing feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回家尽你所能照顾凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go home and take care of Catherine as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治斯 感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Georges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为你的商业伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as your business partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道布萨克不是一个很有耐心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you should know that Boussac is not a very patient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有自己的时间表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has his own timetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 万分感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I am concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 她在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true? She's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔维 她很虚弱 最好是等一等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hervé, she's weak. It's best to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我必须和她谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I must talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you will soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天不可以 她现在脑子还很迷糊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not today. She's too confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问起我了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she ask about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问起我了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she ask about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她患上了失忆症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's suffering from amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我必须见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I have to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我失去你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I'd lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切听起来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It all sounds--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说什么都很愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's so foolish to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 让她休息吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's let her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She knows I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我失去你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I'd lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 接下来的72小时内我们都不能上街\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we can't be on the streets for the next 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 风头过后我们马上就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't worry. We'll leave immediately after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑后 我们会偷偷送走让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will sneak out Jean after it is dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们都会离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then we will all leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳 握住我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my hand, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我另一个学生的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me the name of the other student,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这一切就会停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all this will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握住我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂 你好  - 迪奥先生 我有个好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes? Hello. - I have good news, Monsieur Dior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我 你是哪位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me. Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命运在呼叫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is your destiny calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经为你的新工作室 找到了一个完美的地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have identified the perfect location for your new atelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后乔治斯维格鲁会给你打电话约个时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Georges Vigouroux will call you later and set up an appointment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看工作室的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to see the location for the atelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萨克先生 乔治斯知道我需要一 两天的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mr. Boussac. Georges knows I need another day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Dior,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚定不移地想把你的构想变成现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am unflinching in my desire to turn your vision into a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你必须做好应做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you have to do your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这是一门生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a business, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道 还有相信我 我真的很感激你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I know. And believe me, I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我该说的都说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Then all that needed to be said already has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 战争即将结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}War is ending, Monsieur Dior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候开始新生活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for life to begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我感到希望是很罕见的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, it's unusual for me to feel hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知怎么地 你做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet, somehow, you made that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有韦特海默兄弟的消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard from the Wertheimers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 还没 - 太可笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not yet. - This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毁了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to ruin them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事你需要明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 过去的事不会回头给我们造成困扰 - 你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nothing can come back to haunt us. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要和韦特海默兄弟开战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you are going to go to war with the Wertheimers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的秘密就会公之于众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then all the skeletons are going to come out of the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么是没告诉我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, is there anything you haven't told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有...什么也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No. There is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么秘密是我不知道的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any secrets that I don't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再问同样的问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop asking the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你今天不给他们打电话要求回复 我会打给他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't call them today and demand a reply, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 听起来你遇到麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear. Sounds like you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔莎 不要说我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't start, Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生命中所拥有的一切都是我挣来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the things I have in life, I earned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我白手起家建立了香奈儿公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I built the House of Chanel from nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈儿5号香水是我发明的 是我给他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Chanel No. 5, I invented it. I brought it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他们以为偷了我的东西就能逃脱惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now they think they can get away with stealing it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁想从你这偷走它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who wants to steal it from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮埃尔韦特海默和他那愚蠢的弟弟保罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pierre Wertheimer and his stupid brother Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们逃不掉的 我会得到我应得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They aren't gonna get away with it. I will get what I'm owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我完全赞成人们得到他们应得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. I'm all in favor of people getting what they're owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今晚的派对会很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like it's going to be quite a good party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收到邀请函了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you get your invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的邀请函 没有 为什么这么问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My invitation? No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店的所有客人都收到邀请函了 前台给了我一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the hotel guests are invited. I got given one at the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不去参加派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去  让我们来看看上面写了什么 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not? Let's see what it says, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“尊敬的客人和未来的朋友...”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Distinguished guests and future friends"--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺贴心的 有点受宠若惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's quite sweet. Kind of flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“这么多年过去了 我们都没什么值得庆祝的事”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"After so many years with nothing to celebrate"--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我们诚挚地邀请您 与我们一同为生活举杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You are cordially invited to come and raise a glass to life with us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是今天下午4点到午夜的任何时刻”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}today anytime from 4:00 p.m. to midnight."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不认识这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't know these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我认为你认识他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, I think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“期待与您相识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Looking forward to making your acquaintance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮埃尔韦特海默夫妇”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. and Mrs. Pierre Wertheimer."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太搞笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是这么写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what it says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是巧合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他没有回应的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why he hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 他在玩游戏 但这是场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, he's playing games, but this is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要指引\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情有点不太对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是...凯瑟琳不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just... Catherine is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她会变 但却变得让人认不出了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew she would be changed, but she's unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁认不出  - 我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To whom? - To me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想象她一定经历过什么样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep imagining the things she must have gone through,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在脑海中看到的场景是那么的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the scenarios that I see in my mind are so--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残忍 那么的阴冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're merciless and so bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她在怪你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you feel she blames you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在怪我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开的话 你会更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's safer for you if I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我可以和其他学生待在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can stay with the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家来说 这样更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's safer for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我们目前的报告可确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our reports now confirm that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在巴拉德射击场处决五名学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all five students will be executed at the Balard shooting range.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳 我需要你去传些消息 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine, I need you to deliver some messages, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要让她去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't send her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须试一试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去见凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring me to Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入派对后 由我来带头 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we get inside the party, let me take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟皮埃尔谈多久都行 他已经结婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can talk to Pierre as much as you want. He's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找未婚人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm looking for someone more available.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝酒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人问起我们是怎么认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if anyone asks how you and I know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉他们我们是老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just tell them we're old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争前就认识了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你做什么 都不要提及任何尤为复杂的话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you do, don't mention any of the more complicated issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要提像马德里那样复杂的话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No complicated issues like Madrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你懂我的意思 对吧  - 我当然懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know what I mean, right? - Yes, I certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来看望我一生中最亲密的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just here visiting one of my dearest friends in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整件事就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我 请让开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know me. Please step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 很抱歉 我们需要确认名单上的所有名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do apologize, mademoiselle. We need to confirm all names on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可香奈儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coco Chanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 对不起 名单上没有可可香奈儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, mademoiselle. There is no Coco Chanel on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有邀请函\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“艾尔莎隆巴尔迪小姐”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Miss Elsa Lombardi."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你的名字就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Your name is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 今晚很高兴见到你 - 我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So good to see you this evening. - You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 请这边走 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please. Right this way. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她呢 不是所有的客人都被邀请了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what about her? Aren't all the hotel guests invited?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎所有的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韦特海默先生亲自核准了客人名单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wertheimer personally approved the guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信只是弄混了或其它什么原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm sure it's just been some sort of mix-up or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 我们里面见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in there, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受这种做法 我要进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't acceptable. I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进去 你没有邀请函\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not you. You don't have an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想叫保安过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to have to call security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 你这个小小的令人讨厌的野蛮人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you touch me, you tiny, little beast of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 这是个私人派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mademoiselle, this is a private party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你和其他未被邀请的客人一起进餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're welcome to dine with the other guests that weren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你为此丢掉工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will have you fired for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我 我来试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可悲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 欢迎你们 我是皮埃尔韦特海默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome, everyone. I am Pierre Wertheimer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你们能参加此次派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is so good you are all here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同庆祝世界繁荣与和平的新篇章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to celebrate the new chapter of prosperity and peace in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请为所有聚集在这里的人举杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please raise a glass to all of us who have gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮埃尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pierre.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能来参加我的派对真是太遗憾了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a shame you couldn't come to my party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你进去遇到麻烦了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you have trouble getting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是你才离开的那个超棒的派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean the fabulous party you just left
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就可以过来跟我说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that you could come talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个派对 我抱歉没邀请你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, that one. I apologize for your lack of invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我弟弟收到你寄来的信件了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So my brother and I got your little letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是威胁要起诉我们的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one threatening to sue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表达十分清晰 接近专业水平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite articulate actually. Almost professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会确保你把欠我的还给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure you give me what you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 但我不这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你援用雅利安人法逼我们出局的小把戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That little stunt you pulled invoking the Aryan laws to force us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以随时按下按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can push the button anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个消息传播出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on spreading the word about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别提你住在丽兹的多少个晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention your many nights at the Ritz
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都用来招待那些踢正步的小丑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spent entertaining those goose-stepping clowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说话时别走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't walk away from me when I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要起诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm suing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经靠我的名字和香水发了财\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've made a fortune out of my name and fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起做生意二十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Twenty years we've been doing business together,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你觉得你能偷走我的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now you think you can steal from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们法庭上见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你那可怜的弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and your pathetic brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事永远不会发生 我们不会允许的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That will never happen. We won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我的 你这个该死的白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You owe me, you fucking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之前达成了协议 你 我和我弟弟一起达成的很好的协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We made a deal. You, me and my brother. A good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:24:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你会惹上什么麻烦 而我们也遵守了协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You knew what you were getting into, and we kept our end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分到了属于你的10% 我不知道你为什么总是抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got your 10%. I don't know why you keep complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 因为你骗了我 - 通过支持你 通过相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Because you tricked me! - By backing you? Believing in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说正经的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 你连自己公司的潜力都没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, you couldn't even see the potential of your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.24,0:24:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 现在你把这都归功于自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, you take credit for it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.53,0:24:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时你却很乐意将其出售\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but back then you were more than happy to pass it off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就可以和你那些白痴的朋友聚会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so you could go party with your idiot friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子 你这个肮脏的 令人讨厌的骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liar. You dirty, stinking liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Admit it. Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把公司给了一对犹太人 是因为你知道我们能让你赚大钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave your business to a pair of Jews because you knew we would make you rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人只擅长做这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all you people are good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.51,0:24:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到我说的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱...你们只会赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Money, money, money. All you are is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This conversation isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮埃尔 你从未懂我 你永远都不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never understood me, Pierre, and you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受你的派对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjoy your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.54,0:25:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your body is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的灵魂在别处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your spirit is elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.18,0:25:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不想再继续了 - 我之前也这样觉得 但之后事情就发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't think I want to continue. - That's how I felt. And then it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德拉哈耶夫人在幻象中看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame Delahaye saw you in a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她看到我了  - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She saw me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She knew that you would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.19,0:25:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做没意义 对任何事都没意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no meaning to this, to any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.49,0:25:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在看到你在那里的画面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see you there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都很痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone was suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.58,0:25:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另外还有个人和你在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's someone else with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是单独折磨我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They tortured us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.25,0:25:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在浴室看到的可不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I see in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那个浴室知道些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you know about that bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.51,0:25:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你握住了对方的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You took their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.93,0:25:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握住我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:26:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人帮你活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They helped you survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.18,0:26:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你独自一人在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但那里... - 够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But there-- - That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.61,0:26:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥把你带到我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your brother has brought you to me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也许 能给你那颗烦恼的心带来些许慰藉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that I might bring some solace to a troubled heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.58,0:26:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有人跟你在一起 你握住了对方的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was someone with you. You took their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.21,0:26:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我为你经历的一切感到抱歉 - 德拉哈耶夫人 走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm so sorry for what you went through... - Come, Madame Delahaye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.71,0:26:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 亲爱的 - 下次再说 非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ...my dear - Another time. And thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.46,0:26:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀 带她离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christian, get her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.49,0:27:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.12,0:27:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥先生说他不来了吗  我们计划去看房产的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Monsieur Dior say he's not coming? We are scheduled to visit properties.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.92,0:27:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 取消预约 - 好的 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cancel the appointment. - All right, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.34,0:27:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萨克先生会不高兴的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Boussac will not be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.59,0:27:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.93,0:27:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是想帮你 我们都只是想帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was just trying to help you. We all just want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.10,0:27:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.27,0:27:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们帮不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.19,0:27:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.94,0:27:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在和我们在这里 你必须和我们在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here now with us. You have to be here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我帮你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.28,0:27:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 让的遭遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my fault, what happened to Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不该让他离开这间公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have asked him to leave this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.08,0:27:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.25,0:27:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得原谅自己 当时那种情况 他不可能留在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must forgive yourself. It was an impossible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.71,0:27:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur? Mademoiselle?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前想来看你 我听说你的情况不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to come see you. I heard you were not doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.34,0:28:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我之前打过电话 - 不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I called earlier. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.55,0:28:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想跟你谈谈 - 不行 不见客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I wanted to speak to you. - No. No visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.56,0:28:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人 现在不是时候 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a good time, young man. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen your face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.52,0:28:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么认识你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.48,0:28:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是让的朋友 我听说你回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a friend of Jean. I heard that you were home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.99,0:28:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮个忙 跟我走一趟好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you do me the favor of coming with me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西要给你看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something I need to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳 你身体不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catherine, you are in no condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.16,0:28:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I think it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.13,0:28:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.01,0:28:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他们所在的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.92,0:28:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.93,0:28:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 让和其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Jean and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一共有六个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were six of us total.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.22,0:28:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在我祖母的房子里 安装了一台小型印刷机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We set up a small printing press in my grandmother's house
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.85,0:28:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就开始分发反纳粹的传单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and started distributing anti-Nazi leaflets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.69,0:28:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初 这么做似乎没什么影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the beginning, it seemed like it wouldn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.98,0:29:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但随着影响力日渐增大 抵抗军不断壮大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it grew. The Resistance grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.78,0:29:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便引起了纳粹敌对势力的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then it caught the attention of the Nazi counterparts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我的五个朋友都被纳粹抓走时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When all five of my friends were taken by the Nazis,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确信下一个会是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought for sure I would be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.34,0:29:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没人来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then no one came for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.09,0:29:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 我是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the next day, I was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.47,0:29:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my family was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的那天我们也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the day after that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我就知道 我的朋友们不会说出我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's when I knew my friends would not name me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友没有供出我 你也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends did not break, and you did not break.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.99,0:29:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是如何 在重重折磨下保持缄默的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not know how you kept silent through all the torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.49,0:29:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来感谢你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.66,0:29:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你一条命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.97,0:30:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我第二次重新生活的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave me a second chance to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.89,0:30:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备好了我就送你回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will take you home when you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.70,0:30:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.00,0:30:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在能想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在集中营里 人们不敢相信 我是有多勇敢才能在折磨中活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the camp people couldn't believe how brave I was to survive the torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是因为勇敢我才没有说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it wasn't bravery that kept me from talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.39,0:30:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是胆量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.35,0:30:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你 克里斯汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was you, Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.08,0:31:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.92,0:31:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.63,0:31:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们能杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish they would kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.97,0:31:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉并不难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dying is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.47,0:31:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你知道自己该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only you know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.94,0:31:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见我说话吗 你在跟谁说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you hear me? Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.74,0:31:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你没什么可说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have nothing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.45,0:31:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get her! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.16,0:31:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.33,0:32:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.44,0:32:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.82,0:32:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 克里斯汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No bother, Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.15,0:32:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...我想告诉你 很抱歉我爽约了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just-- I wanted to tell you I'm sorry for missing our meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.99,0:32:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我明天和以后的每一天都会在那\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I will be there tomorrow and every day thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.33,0:32:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得相信你能靠得住 - 我不会让你失望的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need to be able to count on you. - I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.58,0:32:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会一起创造出伟大的东西 你 我和布萨克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll make something great together. You, me and Boussac.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很难得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's rare, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.67,0:32:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.97,0:32:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得人生的第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To get a second chance in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.56,0:32:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Second chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我得到了第二次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. I have been given a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.85,0:33:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们都得到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.58,0:33:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔莎 去你自己的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find your own room, Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.04,0:33:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没心情听你胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not in the mood for your bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.13,0:33:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.77,0:33:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想干吗  - 你说得很对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you want? - You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.86,0:33:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未懂你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never understood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.82,0:33:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 皮埃尔 - 但我想了解你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pierre. - But I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.29,0:34:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.31,0:34:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coco, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.11,0:34:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是我弟弟干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not me. It's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.83,0:34:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乖乖听话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So then be a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.67,0:34:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的钱给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And pay me my fucking money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.34,0:36:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译:王国萱

